-- Madagascar Water, Energy Tariffs to Rise by 25%, l’Express Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-02-21T06:31:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/madagascar-water-energy-tariffs-to-rise-by-25-l-express-says.html
Madagascar plans to increase water
and electricity costs by as much as 25 percent, Antananarivo-
based  l’Express de Madagascar  reported, citing government
officials it didn’t identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
